            <h1>Minister of Health and Care Services Anne-Grete Strøm-Erichsen</h1>
            <h2>Anne-Grete Strøm-Erichsen</h2>
             
            <a href="/en/dep/hod/About-the-Ministry/minister-of-health-and-care-services-ann.html?id=582304" class="last">About the minister</a>
