<div class="ArticleView">
        <img src="/upload/HOD/Ingresssbilder/norge-russland-ingress.jpg" alt="" class="ArticleImg" />
        
        
        <div class="ArticleImgContent">
            <h2><a href="/en/dep/hod/press-center/pressemeldinger/2009/russia-takes-over-the-chairmanship-of-th.html?id=587097">Russia takes over the chairmanship of the health collaboration under the Northern Dimension</a></h2>        
                
            <p>
               November 25 Norway hosted the Northern Dimension Partnership in Public Health and Social Well-being’s Annual Conference. At the conference, Russia formally took over the chairmanship of the Partnership from Norway. 
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    
    

<div class="ingressView">
    
    
        
                   
        
        
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/hod/Whats-new/News/2010/Joint-communiqe-by-The-Ministers-of-Health-of-the-Foreign-Policy-and-Global-Health-Initiative.html?id=605251" title="">
                        Joint communiqe by The Ministers of Health of the Foreign Policy and Global Health Initiative
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">Geneva, 18th May 2010</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[20.05.2010]</p>
                <p>The Ministers of Health of the Foreign Policy and Global Health (FPGH) Initiative, comprising Brazil, France, Indonesia, Norway, Senegal, South Africa and Thailand, met on the sidelines of the 63rd World Health Assembly in Geneva today to discuss current global health challenges, particularly the importance of achieving the health-related Millennium Development Goals (MDGs), ahead of the upcoming MDG Summit in New York in September 2010.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
