                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/hod/kampanjer/the-coordination-reform.html?id=524777" title="">
                        The Coordination Reform
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[17.10.2008]</p>
                <p>In the course of April 2009 the Minister of Health and Social Affairs Bjarne Håkon Hanssen will present a new health reform, a coordination reform, for the health service. The minister’s own team of experts will help him to find the economic and legal tack for meeting the challenges in the Norwegian health sector.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
